   predates it, but is added here as the real-world era beginning 2019-05-01.
   UTF-8 byte sequences:
     Meiji  E6 98 8E E6 B2 BB   Taisho E5 A4 A7 E6 AD A3
     Showa  E6 98 AD E5 92 8C   Heisei E5 B9 B3 E6 88 90
     Reiwa  E4 BB A4 E5 92 8C */
static const territory_era japan_eras[5] =
