/* Notes: (1) the asm sets "JapaneseEras SETL {TRUE}" enabling Japanese era
 * (gengou) year rendering; this is now carried in calendar.eras / num_eras
 * (see japan_eras above).  (2) The IME SWI chunk (JapanIMESWI_Base = &52500)
 * is carried in territory_data.ime_chunk.  (3) The kanji literal for "year" in
 * the date format is U+5E74 (E5 B9 B4), transcribed from
 * "%ce%yr<kanji>%m3%zdy<kanji>" in the asm. */
